Note on ROM images: the files under roms/ (Wozmon, Apple Integer BASIC, the
Apple Cassette Interface ROM, the character generator ROM) and disks/ (ONEDOS)
are historical Apple-1 firmware and third-party software included for
preservation and interoperability. They are not covered by the MIT license
above, which applies only to the emulator's own source code.
